ZH:我刚收到一张来自北京的明信片。
EN:I just received a postcard from Beijing.

ZH:请帮我买些明信片，我想给朋友们寄明信片。
EN:Please help me buy some postcards, I want to send postcards to my friends.

ZH:这张明信片上画了一只可爱的小猫。
EN:There is a cute little cat painted on this postcard.

ZH:明信片上是一幅山水画。
EN:There is a landscape painting on the postcard.

ZH:每次我旅行，我都会寄明信片给家人。
EN:Every time I travel, I send postcards to my family.

ZH:请问明信片邮费是多少？
EN:May I ask how much is the postage for a postcard?

ZH:我正在找一张特别的明信片送给我的父母。
EN:I am looking for a special postcard to give to my parents.

ZH:这些明信片有中国的名胜古迹。
EN:These postcards have famous scenic spots in China.

ZH:我在明信片上写下了我对你的思念。
EN:I wrote down my longing for you on the postcard.

ZH:我把明信片贴在了我的墙上。
EN:I put the postcard on my wall.

ZH:这些明信片是纪念香港的。
EN:These postcards are souvenirs of Hong Kong.

ZH:明信片上有一段友谊的寄语。
EN:There is a message of friendship on the postcard.

ZH:这是我第一次给别人寄明信片。
EN:This is my first time sending a postcard to someone.

ZH:我清点了一下，我共收到了15张明信片。
EN:I counted, and I received a total of 15 postcards.

ZH:我在明信片背后写下了我的旅行经历。
EN:I wrote down my travel experience on the back of the postcard.

ZH:这家书店有很多种类的明信片。
EN:This bookstore has a variety of postcards.

ZH:我很喜欢收到明信片，因为它们让我感到特别。
EN:I really like receiving postcards because they make me feel special.

ZH:这个明信片很特别，因为是朋友亲手画的。
EN:This postcard is very special because it was hand-drawn by a friend.

ZH:我把家乡的美景都拍在了明信片上。
EN:I took pictures of the beautiful scenery of my hometown and put them on postcards.

ZH:这张明信片寄自法国，是我兄弟旅行时给我的。
EN:This postcard is from France, it was given to me by my brother when he was traveling.
